main event: On December 7, 1969, a 13-year-old civilian observed an unidentified flying object for approximately 20 minutes in Round Lake, Illinois.
interesting points: The observer did not provide detailed information about the observation,The object passed over the observer's car at a height of approximately 200 ft.,The object was described as round and silver with a rim around the outer edge,The object made no sound during the sighting,The conclusion of the report stated that there was insufficient data to draw any conclusions.
